t: هل مديرك مجنون ؟ ! : الدليل الحاسم في كيفية التعامل مع مديرك
Athar al-nahdah al-'ilmiyah al-hadithah 'ala al-fikr al-qanuni : dirasah fi falsafat al-qanun
Al-tanzim al-qanuni li-al-ahzab al-siyasiyah bayna al-nazariyah wa-al-tatbiq
Al-tatawwur al-dusturi wa-al-tashri'i li-al-jam'iyat al-ahliyah : dirasah muqaranah
Al-ruuyah al-dawliyah bi-shaun himayat al-tharwat al-bayulujiyah wa-al-ma'arif al-taqldyah : dirasah muqaranah
Al-nizam al-qanuni li-wakil al-'uqud al-tijariyah : tab'ah muzawwadah bi-ahdath al-tashri'at al-qanuniyah wa-al-ahkam al-qadauiyah
Dawr al-dawlah fi himayat al-sirriyah wa-al-istithnauat al-waridah 'alayha ma'a 'ard li-ahamm al-i'lanat wa-al-muutamarat al-duwaliyah wa-mawqif
Al-tanzim al-qanuni lil-sina'at al-dawauiyah 'ala dawu ittifaqiyat al-tiribs
Tajrim al-ittifaq al-jinaui bayna al-mabadiu al-dusturiyah wa-al-i'tibarat al-'amaliyah : dirasah muqaranah
Al-nizam al-qanuni al-dawli li-himayat al-biuah min al-adrar al-najimah 'an al-aslihah al-nuwawiyah
Ahkam al-daman al-'ayni wa-al-shakhsi wa-al-markaz al-qanuni lil-kafil al-'ayni
Al-daf' bi-al-jahl aw 'adam al-'ilm wa-atharuhu fi al-khusumat al-qadauiyah al-mukhtalifah
Al-wasit fi ta'amulat al-ajanib ma'a maslahat al-shahr al-'aqari wa-al-tawthiq
Awjuh al-butlan fi ijrauat al-tahqiq al-ibtidaui
